4 · Storage &amp; retrieval

Raw files: gs://chopin/videos_raw/UUID.webm
Processed (optional transcode) into videos_hls/UUID/playlist.m3u8

- 

video_transcode_worker.py – Cloud-Run job converts WebM → HLS 480p.

- 

Once transcode done, worker emits WebSocket video_ready event; VideoPanel subscribes &amp; auto-refreshes list.

5 · Physics / bandwidth budget

- 

Target bit-rate 2 Mbps → 15 MB/min.

